Fit V2 Board Support and Distro for i.MX


To create an image build directory and environment for Fit imx, source the 'fit-setup-build.sh' script.

Usage: source fit-setup-build.sh [-b build-dir] [-h]
  options:
    -b build-dir    set build directory (def: build)
    -h              print usage


The environment is configured for DISTRO=speedy and MACHINE=fit-v2.
